imdb.plot outline: Planet Crouton Entertainment is a sketch-comedy web series that features 12 different characters who all star in their own shows. You'll meet a talking pig, workout instructor, lumberyard worker, an old-lady, waitress, DJ, pop star, vampire, actress, and computer tech. They all live in their wacky worlds that together makeup Planet Crouton.
